| name = Point puller
| class = PointPuller
| doomednum = 5002
}}[[Classes]]: <u>PointPuller</u><br>

A point puller pulls nearby actors towards it. This force crosses sector boundaries, decreases linearly with distance, and is felt within a circle centered on itself. The force is felt only if the point puller can see the target object. To push actors away, see [[Classes:PointPusher|PointPusher]].

The [[sector]] in which the thing is placed must have the “Pusher Enabled” bit set, see [[sector specials]].

